⚖️ Frame dependence matters too

Relativity literally says:

* speed depends on reference frame

A car:

* stationary relative to itself
* moving relative to Earth
* moving very fast relative to the Sun
* moving even faster relative to the galaxy

So:

motion itself is relational.

